entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the fourth Alliance Pilot from the Imperial Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Search the Imperial Detainment Facility for the next Alliance Pilot being held there
entries.task01_task_display_string_1: You defeated the Prison Battle Droids.
entries.task01_task_display_string_2: You defeated the Prison Tracking Probot Droids.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Search the main detention room located at the center of the Detention Facility. The pilot should be in one of the Northern containment bays.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Give the pilot the disguise you have.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Defeat any Prison Droidekas located in the main detention room.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Prisoner Tracking Probot Droids located in the main detention room.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Prison Battle Droids located in the main detention room.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Defeat Imperial Detainment Factility Officers located in the prisoner control room on the North side of the Facility.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Colonel in combat and take his Imperial Officer Uniform.
entries.task09_journal_entry_title: Get the disguise from Colonel Rogen Lithal
